Mysticism					KEY:Trait ~ Mysticism								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait					PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Mysticism]				PRERACE:1,Kitsune																				DESC:You have learned to tap into your inner wellspring of magical power. Once per day when you cast a spell or spell-like ability, you can treat your caster level as 1 higher than your actual caster level. Additionally, increase your maximum age at each category after Youth (including your maximum age) by 10 years each time you have selected the Magical Tail feat. Adjust your aging bonuses and penalties according to your new age category.																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.28
