Omen of Greatness				KEY:Trait ~ Omen of Greatness							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait					PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Omen of Greatness]										PRETEMPLATE:1,Voidkin												DESC:When you were born, your brilliant, white fur was decreed to be an omen of greatness. As a result, your word holds great weight with other kitsune. You receive a +1 trait bonus on Bluff, Diplomacy, and Intimidate checks when dealing with kitsune.																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.28
One Step Ahead				KEY:Trait ~ One Step Ahead							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.RaceTrait.KitsuneTrait					PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ One Step Ahead]			PRERACE:1,Kitsune																				DESC:You constantly scheme, to stay ahead of your adversaries. You gain a +1 dodge bonus to your AC against attacks of opportunity.																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.28	ASPECT:CombatBonus|+1 dodge bonus to your AC against vs. of opportunity
